Package: EpiViz
Type: Package
Title: EpiViz
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Matthew", "Lee", email = "matthew.lee@bristol.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An implementation of Circos plots for epidemiologists in R. It takes the Circlize package and adapts it for use by epidemiologists.
    Circos plots provide an informative way of plotting greater than 50 plotting points. A legend can be plotted automatically and customised.
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
